  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A single-center cohort of patients with acute ischemic stroke and transient ischemic attack
      who admitted to the Severance hospital of Yonsei university and their long-term outcomes.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      This is a single-center cohort of consecutive patients with acute ischemic stroke and
      transient ischemic attack who admitted to the Severance hospital of Yonsei university in
      Republic of Korea.

      Stroke recurrence, Cardiovascular event, all cause mortality and cardiovascular mortality
      were collected through long-term follow up.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
